summary: This is a brief email correspondence regarding the completion of a photo sourcing project, with an attached document containing evidence item numbers, CD names, and location information. The document is subject to a protective order covering specific paragraphs.
keyFacts: A photo sourcing project was completed and attached to the email on September 30, 2021.
The attached document includes three columns: Evidence Item #, Name of CD, and Location of Item.
The document is subject to a protective order covering paragraphs 7, 8, 9, 10, 15, and 17.
The email is part of the Epstein case document set (EFTA00159783) and references another document (EFTA_00010132).
